const Teams = ({employees}) => { let nothing = false; const addedTeam = [ {teamName: "TeamA"}, {teamName: "TeamB"}, {teamName: "TeamC"} ]; return( <>
    { addedTeam.map((employee, index) =>
    {employee.teamName}
    { employees.map((e)=> e.teamName === employee.teamName && nothing ? (

    Name: {e.fullName}

    Designation: {e.designation}

    ) : e.teamName === '' ? (

    {employee.teamName} has no member.

    ) : null ) }
    ) }
) } export default Teams;
